{"tid":1129092,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"瑧樺超購近6倍　提價加推102伙","createTime":"2019-04-28T09:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T03:49:38.000Z","uid":209853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"677ca1c60bddfdb832d1942e94b344051862a0da","tid":1129092,"uid":209853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T09:07:48.000Z","msg":"真係抵買？<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190428/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190428%2F&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0Kyvnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=85fc9654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190428/</a><br />\nbkn-20190428155258645-0428_00842_001.html[/url]"},{"pid":"cf52ef002a3c88ce1b554dd5ef78f2ad31a13c56","tid":1129092,"uid":209853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T09:08:34.000Z","msg":"新世界發展(00017)等合作發展的何文田瑧樺於上周五(4月26日)開始接受網上認購登記。消息指，截至今日(28日)下午3時，暫時累收約600票，超額認購近6倍。 <br />\n<br />\n因應市場反應，發展商剛提價加推2號價單共102伙，擬最快周末開售，預料有機會再度加推，銷售安排將於短期內公布。 <br />\n<br />\n新價單包括35伙開放式、42伙一房戶，以及25伙兩房戶，實用面積204至526方呎，首度推出全新A2兩房戶型，逾半單位折實價更低於600萬港元。與首張價單相比，新價單平均提價近2%，折實平均呎價24,787元，售價由501.4萬至1,434.1萬元，折實呎價22,159至27,264元。"},{"pid":"d5cd9df2f81babfe41bbd01e9f0a846f10d0a4ca","tid":1129092,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T09:14:35.000Z","msg":"油麻地？"},{"pid":"d1e0f095499bab2b2bb6b519f4b24c1eacdb7e48","tid":1129092,"uid":108236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"平！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3b123f00782a288023297d0cb31d5acf2d9320","tid":1129092,"uid":122318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T09:39:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾位置都賣咁貴<br />\n個位近馬路好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c163cfcdba757273cc8bc678b1e928a